headline: US Homebuilder Sentiment Ticks Up But Tariffs Weigh on Outlook
summary: (Bloomberg) -- US homebuilder confidence barely rose this month on a pickup in current sales, though demand expectations stumbled to a more than one-year low and prices of construction materials are climbing on the heels of higher tariffs.
